BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC State African American Cultural Center
CATEGORIES:Community Events,Student Life
DESCRIPTION:Drop by the African American Cultural Center Library on weekday
 s from Feb. 9 to 27 to express your "shelf love" and go on a blind date wit
 h a book. We'll have a number of sweet reads curated by our library staff w
 rapped and waiting for you to choose from on our cupid cart. Each book will
  include a dating profile and a custom quote sticker to help you find your 
 next favorite book. After you select your book\, bring it to the circulatio
 n desk to check it out and to receive a book lover's appreciation gift. The
 re will be an assortment of book genres to choose from. Unwrap your book at
  home and return it when you finish reading it.
DTEND:20260223T230000Z
DTSTAMP:20260324T024536Z
DTSTART:20260223T150000Z
GEO:35.785108;-78.674529
LOCATION:Witherspoon Student Center\, African American Cultural Center Libr
 ary (218)
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Shelf Love and Sweet Reads
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51993482407049
URL:https://calendar.ncsu.edu/event/shelf-love-sweet-reads
END:VEVENT
