X-SOURCE:NC State African American Cultural Center
CATEGORIES:Community Events,Student Life
DESCRIPTION:The AYA Ambassadors are taking over What’s on the Table? in Feb
 ruary for special editions of Diaspora Dinners. Come celebrate the richness
  of the African diaspora with us. Each session will feature a curated cultu
 ral cuisine paired with an interactive presentation\, activity or conversat
 ion led by the AYA Ambassadors.
