BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC State African American Cultural Center
CATEGORIES:Community Events,Student Life
DESCRIPTION:Join the African American Cultural Center for a fun evening of 
 great books and even better food. Come ready to explore genre-inspired tabl
 es to discover your reading niche and compete in bingo to win prizes (gift 
 cards). Every table will tell a story and have great treats and food to mat
 ch.  Feed your curiosity and your stomach and make new friends.\n\nAll Afri
 can American Cultural Center programs are open to all students.
DTEND:20260306T000000Z
DTSTAMP:20260324T024536Z
DTSTART:20260305T220000Z
GEO:35.785108;-78.674529
LOCATION:Witherspoon Student Center\, African American Cultural Center (218
 )
SEQUENCE:0
